<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Achrafooxi | Portfolio</title>

<style>
body {
  background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #000000, #1a1a1a, #0d0d0d);
  background-size: 400% 400%;
  animation: bg 10s infinite;
  color: white;
  font-family: Arial;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px;
}

@keyframes bg {
  0% {background-position:0%}
  50% {background-position:100%}
  100% {background-position:0%}
}

h1 {
  font-size: 50px;
  color: #00ffcc;
}

.section {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  padding: 25px;
  margin: 25px auto;
  width: 80%;
  border-radius: 20px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.section:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.skill {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 10px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background: #00ffcc;
  color: black;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

.project {
  margin: 15px;
  padding: 15px;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  border-radius: 10px;
}

/* الأزرار */
.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 15px;
  padding: 15px 30px;
  background: #00ffcc;
  color: black;
  border-radius: 15px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 20px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.btn:hover {
  background: #00cc99;
  transform: scale(1.1);
}

/* زر Instagram خاص */
.ig-btn {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f09433, #dc2743, #bc1888);
  color: white;
}

.ig-btn:hover {
  opacity: 0.8;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>🚀 Benvenuto nel mio Portfolio</h1>

<div class="section">
  <h2>👤 Chi sono</h2>
  <p>Sono achrafooxi</p>
  <p>Sto imparando la programmazione da zero 💪</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>💻 Le mie competenze</h2>
  <div class="skill">HTML</div>
  <div class="skill">CSS</div>
  <div class="skill">JavaScript</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>🚀 I miei progetti</h2>

  <div class="project">💻 Primo sito web</div>
  <div class="project">🎨 Design creativo</div>

</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>📩 Contattami</h2>
  <p>Puoi contattarmi oppure seguirmi:</p>

  <a href="mailto:email@email.com" class="btn">📧 Email</a>

  <a href="https://instagram.com/achrafooxi" target="_blank" class="btn ig-btn">
    📸 Instagram
  </a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
